high_descs: Turn around and walk to the garbage then turn left and walk to the wall then turn left.
Pick up the dirty purple wash cloth that's in front of you.
Turn left and walk to the closest sink then turn left to face it.
Wash the cloth in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and take three steps then turn right and walk to the tub.
Put the wash cloth in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean wash cloth in the tub.

high_descs: take the purple rag from the basin
take the rag to the sink
rinse the rag in the sink then remove
take the rag back to the tub
put the rag in the tub
anns.task_desc: rinse the rag from the tub then put it back

high_descs: Turn around and face the end of the tub where the faucet is.
Pick the purple cloth up from the tub.
Turn left and then to the left again to face the sink on the left.
Put the cloth in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the cloth up again.
Turn around and go right to face the tub.
Put the cloth in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean cloth in a tub.
